Note that the public key may appear in many hub folders. If you want to block a person completely, you have to find all of his or her folders.

@43110: 
1. Cut your files into small parts, and give each part a unique name, like cutting a piece of paper into smaller pieces, and putting numbers on them.
2. Make a `file.json` that tells ZeroMux how to put the pieces together.
(Use the python script at the end of [This Page](/1CiDoBP8RiWziqiBGEd8tQMy66A6fmnw2V/big/docs/))
3. Let ZeroMux put together the pieces of the file for you.
("Registering Event Handlers" section of [This Page](/1CiDoBP8RiWziqiBGEd8tQMy66A6fmnw2V/big/docs/usage/making-file-downloader/))


    var events = initEventObj();
    events.onfinish = finish;
    function finish(blob)
    {
        // `blob` contains the reassembled big file
        var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
        location.href = url;
    }
    downloadBigFile("your/own/file.json", events); // (jsonPath, events)
